<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Teacher Profile</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <style>
        .teacher-profile{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            height: 70vh;
        }
        .teacher-about{
           padding: 5rem;
        }
        .teacher-details, .teacher-image, .teacher-about{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            width: 33%;
        }
        .teacher-details p{
            margin: 0.8rem 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="sidebar">
            <h2>S_T_A_S</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/teacher/profile/<%= teachers._id %>"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i> My profile</a></li>
                <li><a href="/teacher/messages/<%= teachers._id %>"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i> All Messages</a></li>
                <li><a href="/teacher/appointments/<%= teachers._id %>"><i class="fa-regular fa-user"></i> My Appointments</a></li>
                <li><a href="/teacher/appointment-request/<%= teachers._id %>"><i class="fa-solid fa-chalkboard-user"> </i> Appointment Requests</a></li>
                <li><a href="/logout"><i class="fa-solid fa-right-from-bracket"></i> Logout</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="main_content">
            <div class="header"> 
                <p>Welcome!! To Teacher Pannel</p>
                <div class="admin-info">
                    <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/thumbnails/042/891/253/small_2x/professional-teacher-avatar-illustration-for-education-concept-vector.jpg" alt="" height="30px" width="30px" style="border-radius: 50%;">
                    <p>Teacher</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">Profile</h1>
            <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">I am Teacher in XYZ PUBLIC SCHOOL</h2>
            <div class="teacher-profile">
                <div class="teacher-about">
                    <div class="" >
                        <h3 style="padding: 1rem 0;">About me</h3>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Itaque nihil voluptatibus totam, modi inventore laudantium. Porro placeat temporibus ut aliquam praesentium libero, molestias, esse earum culpa laboriosam cumque blanditiis laborum!</p>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="teacher-image"><img src="<%= teachers.teacher_photo || 'https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/police-vector-illustration-officer-policeman-cop-law-security-uniform-patrol-enforcement_1013341-141655.jpg?semt=ais_hybrid' %>" alt="<%= teachers.name %>" width="250px" height="250px" style="border-radius: 50%;" ></div>
                <div class="teacher-details">
                    <div class="">
                        <h3>Details </h3>
                    <p><b>Name : </b></p>
                    <p><%= teachers.name %></p>
                    <p><b>Email :</b></p>
                    <p><%= teachers.email %></p>
                    <p><b>Specialization :</b></p>
                    <p><%= teachers.specialization %></p>
                    <p><b>Portal Password :</b></p>
                    <p><%= teachers.password %></p>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
        
        </body>
        </html>